\par
Each of the four fieldset must have a legend, as indicated above.\par
[required] shown in the list above means that the input must be entered by the user before the form can be successfully submitted, so you must indicate this by adding the appropriate text in the HTML i.e. required\par
For everything in the form except the submit button, there must be an appropriate label which has an appropriate for e.g.\line\par
\par
<label for="avatar">Your image:</label>\par
<input type="file" id="avatar" name="avatar" required>\par
\par
\par
